# These lines make sure Git does NOT ignore them.
# =========================================================
!*.uproject
!Source/
!Source/**

!Config/
!Config/**

!Plugins/
!Plugins/**
!Plugins/**/*.uplugin
!Plugins/**/Source/
!Plugins/**/Source/**
